## Pipeline Overview

### Phase 1 — Staging Deploy

0. Deploy guard (staging app)
1. Pre-deploy validation
2. Push to `main` on GitHub
3. Run `deploy_staging.ps1` (syncs repo, deploys staging app, runs smoke tests, writes gate artifact)
4. Verify staging

### Phase 2 — Prod Deploy (only after Phase 1 passes)

0. Deploy guard (prod app)
1. Verify staging gate artifact exists for current SHA
2. Run `deploy_prod.ps1` (validates gate, requires "PROD" confirmation, syncs repo, deploys prod app, runs read-only smoke tests)
3. Verify prod

